(5062,E'1190 Priory Rd',E'Eau Claire',E'WI',54701,NULL,NULL,E'St. Bede\'s Priory',E'HGA',E'c.1963',E'Received "Award of Merit" for distinguished architecture at the 32nd Annual Convention of the Minnesota Society of Architects (1966); judges cited "the harmony of undisturbed nature and bold, simple, unmistakably man-made forms;" the monastery was sold by the Benedictine order in 2011 to the University of Wisconsin-Eau Claire\'s foundation  and converted into the UW-Eau Claire Children’s Nature Academy.'),
(5063,E'3949 Bethel Dr',E'Arden Hills',E'MN',55112,NULL,NULL,E'Bethel Seminary',E'HGA',E'1963',E'Received "Award of Merit" for distinguished architecture at the 32nd Annual Convention of the Minnesota Society of Architects (1966); judges cited "The group organization is promising and sound with the nodal pavilions furnishing a scintillating relief and purpose at appropriate intervals"; the seminary for 250 was the first phase of a master campus plan for the Baptist college; after the seminary moved, the complex was renamed the Lakeside Center.'),
