(5082,E'5055 Bassett Creek Dr',E'Golden Valley',E'MN',55422,NULL,NULL,E'Thomas B. Hendrix Residence',E'Hendrix, Thomas B.',E'1960',E'Architect\'s own house; personal home of Thomas B Hendrix and his family until 2013. It had a pyramid-shaped roof over a courtyard; in 2016, current owners removed pyramid-shaped roof from 1980s sunroom addition and replaced with a rectangular roof that still blends with the house. Featured on 2018 Tour Day.'),
