(5145,E'540 Warwick St',E'St Paul',E'MN',55116,NULL,NULL,E'Derham Hall II',E'Unknown',E'1962',E'Second home for the all-girls Catholic School (original Derham Hall, built in 1905, is located on the campus of St Kate\'s and listed on the NRHP); the $1M classroom building was built to accommodate 600 students; two stories in the front (west side) sloping down to three stories on the rear (east).'),
