(5159,E'1532 Trollhagen Dr NE',E'Fridley',E'MN',55421,NULL,NULL,E'House',E'Rodney W. Billman, Builder',E'1966',E'Home-builder Billman built it for a close friend, who he met in basic training during military service; large rambler backing a pond; a second attached garage was added later. Billman developed this entire neighborhood, and later built himself a unique home down the street at 5179 St Imier Dr).'),
