(5261,E'496 Bootleg Lake Rd SW',E'Bemidji',E'MN',56601,NULL,NULL,E'House',E'Unknown',E'1969',E'The exterior of this house is very Rapsonian (especially the roofline), and resembles his "Red Cedar House" (1966) that commissioned by the Weyerhaeuser Company for the Jonathan development; that home was reportedly in Better Homes & Gardens, although the interior of this house only vaguely mimics the original. Sited well on an large property between Bootleg Lake and Little Boot Lake.'),
