(5641,E'2112 Folwell Ave',E'Falcon Heights',E'MN',55108,NULL,NULL,E'Donald C. Rasmusson Residence',E'Unknown',E'1966',E'Featured as an illustration of the Contemporary style with front-gabled roof in Virginia McAlester\'s "A Field Guide to American Houses" (2013 ed.), which noted "the wall cladding is applied in vertical strips with windows set into separate material. This was often a cost-saving device." At the time of construction, Rasmusson was a professor in the Dept. of Agronomy and Plant Genetics.'),
