(5676,E'2400 Pascal St',E'Roseville',E'MN',55113,NULL,NULL,E'Oscar J. Husby Residence',E'Unknown',E'1965',E'Builder\'s own home: Husby was part of family business O.J. Husby & Sons with father Ole and brother Joe; this is in one of their developments: Husby\'s Northview addition.  Brickwork and masonry were their calling card.  This bi-level takes advantage of lake view across road; very handsome doorknobs on front entrance.'),
