(5860,E'2212 Minnehaha Ave',E'Minneapolis',E'MN',55404,NULL,NULL,E'A.A. Equipment Co.',E'Engler, Irwin E.',E'1965*',E'Store building for repair shop for a butcher machinery and refrigeration service; Owner/Builder: Walter W. Pohl.; 1958 addition for the A.A. Saw Co. (Builder: August Cederstrand); 1965 partial teardown for a new add\'n designed by engineer Marshall Cederstrand (builder: August Cederstrand Co.); 1966 add\'n by Irwin E. Engler for what was then renamed A.A. Equipment Co. (Builder: Belair Corp.)'),
